      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRESIDENT ROLEX (2) is a handy dog who jumped from box 2 last time out and scored by half a length at Wentworth Park (29.93). Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and two minor placings from nine starts. Looks the one to beat. HOT SHOT ETHICS (1) is worth forgiving for his last effort when eighth (30.42) at Wentworth Park over 520m. Form here is sound including seven wins. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Leading chance. RISE UP NISMO (4) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 1.75 lengths second (25.01) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Safe beginner who will go forward from trap two. Can turn it around this time. JAKEY BLUE (8) missed the frame latest (25.30) when fourth over 450m at this track in a Grade 5. Already a winner from this draw.",
